title: MASH Season 6 - No Canned Laughter - h.264 aac HQ [SlipTV]
description:
Finally, a MASH release without canned laughter. Ripped by me personally in high quality h.264, these episodes come straight from the UK DVD box set.


Watch using VLC, or any other media player that supports MKV/h.264 (all the decent codec packs support it).

So far the first six seasons are up, 7 will be up once this one has enough seeds and 8 is currently ripping. I'm watching the episodes before I upload them to check for quality, so I can guarantee that everything I upload is glitch free.
